short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Download osu maps from various mirror APIs

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A lightweight extension for osu! players to download the beatmaps from third-party sites for the game without manually visiting the third-party sites or installing the third-party site application.

Mirror download APIs:
- Mino
- Osu direct
- Nerinyan
- beatconnect 

Tip: pin the extension on your browser for the convenience for quick API switching
